{{! Refer lecture code to learn more on how this works
don't forget to include your css and your client-side script file references in the layout.
for the theme, you can simply read the themePreference for the user and inject it into the body element }}


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body class="{{themePreference}}">
    <main>
        {{{body}}}
    </main>
</body>

</html>



